                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <placeName>Montreal</placeName>\n                                        <date>8<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> January 5611</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>\n                                        <addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                                        <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Dear Sir</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(3)\">The kindly feeling always exhibited<lb/> by you\n                                        towards me during my residence in\n                                                  <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName><lb/> emboldens\n                                        me to request of you now the favor that<lb/> you will please\n                                        acquaint me at the earliest possible opportunity<lb/> with\n                                        the name of any established respectable congregation\n                                        requiring the services<lb/> of a person to act as Hazan\n                                        (after the German Minhag)<lb/> Shochet and Mohel in either\n                                        or all capacities, as I think<lb/> it more than probable I\n                                        shall be leaving my present situation<lb/> in\n                                                  <date>May</date> next. I can procure the necessary\n                                        testimonials<lb/> as to my fitness for such offices in\n                                        addition to those already<lb/> in my possession. Should you\n                                        not know at present any<lb/> Congregation requiring the\n                                        services of such a person you<lb/> would confer a favor on\n                                        me by inserting in the next number<lb/> of the Occident the\n                                        enclosed advertisement to be continued<lb/> until\n                                        countermanded. Of course the charges for the same<lb/> which\n                                        I am told will not be high I will readily pay<lb/> upon your\n                                        so requiring either to your agent here <persName>Mr J H<lb/>\n                                                  Joseph</persName> or to any other of your friends\n                                        you may name.<lb/> Perhaps you would be kind enough to\n                                        permit all<lb/> applications to be addressed to you, as you\n                                        have done with<lb/> other individuals. I must beg further to\n                                        trespass on<lb/> your kindness and request you to favor me\n                                        with a line<lb/> so soon as your numerous engagements<lb/>\n                                        will permit</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3zg6gt29/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
